e earth"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the goods, conveniences,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comforts, of life;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadobN","text_ar":"جَدْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (JK, S, Msb;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruitfulness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"increase; plenty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundance of good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of good things:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] truffles are included in the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSobN","text_ar":"خِصْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and also locusts, when they come after the herbage has dried up and the people are secure from being injured by them. (AHn.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baladN xiSobN","text_ar":"بَلَدٌ خِصْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoSaAbN","text_ar":"اَخْصَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baladN sabosabN","text_ar":"بَلَدٌ سَبْسَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaAsibu","text_ar":"سَبَاسِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., the sing. being used [in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bld AxSAb","text_ar":"بلد اخصاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as a pl., as though made to consist of parts, or portions, [each termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSobN","text_ar":"خِصْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"region, abounding with herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the produce